item.title: Dreamers

item.content:encoded:
We need to find God, and he cannot be found in noise and restlessness. God is the friend of silence. See how nature - trees, flowers, grass- grows in silence ; see the stars, the moon and the sun, how they move in silence... We need silence to be able to touch souls.</br>
Let us touch the dying, the poor, the lonely and the unwanted according to the graces we have received and let us not be ashamed or slow to do the humble work.
